    main.features
      header.features-hero.center
        .container
          h1.white Boost Your Career Growth

      section.features-items.center
        .container
          .features-items__section
            p.features-items--heading.bold Automated Resume Parsing
            p Upload your CV in any format and get an automated parser-friendly CV instantly. We have three convenient options for you to upload your CV:
            .row.parsing
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/parsing-create.jpg", alt="parsing create")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/parsing-link.jpg", alt="parsing link")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/parsing-upload.jpg", alt="parsing upload")
          .features-items--separator
          .features-items__section
            p.features-items--heading.bold Instant Video CV Creation
            p Get a video CV to attract recruiters and opportunities and stand out in the job market instantly.  We help you create a video CV in four  simple steps:
            .row
              img(src="../assets/img/video-cv-creation.jpg", alt="video cv creation")
          .features-items--separator
          .features-items__section
            p.features-items--heading.bold Personalised Job Search
            p Find befitting opportunities, using our filter optimised job search engine, matching your location, domain, job-type, experience level and salary requirements instantly.
            .row.job-search
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/job-search-1.jpg", alt="job search")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/job-search-2.jpg", alt="job search")
          .features-items--separator
          .features-items__section
            p.features-items--heading.bold Adaptive Event Feed
            p Find meetups, hangouts, conferences and workshops near you where you can engage with like-minded fellows and expand your network and reach wider bases.
            .row.events
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/event-1.jpg", alt="event")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/event-2.jpg", alt="event")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/event-3.jpg", alt="event")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/event-4.jpg", alt="event")
          .features-items--separator
          .features-items__section
            p.features-items--heading.bold Integrated Referrals and Reward System
            p Make your job-hunting experience extremely fun by earning reward points. Build your profile, refer fellow candidates and earn points at each step to be redeemed at our partner brands to enjoy your job search.
            .row.rewards
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/reward-1.jpg", alt="reward")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/reward-2.jpg", alt="reward")
              .flex-1
                img(src="../assets/img/reward-3.jpg", alt="reward")


    footer.footer.center
      .container
        p.italic
          span.bold Powered by
          |  T_Steps: The Talent Engagement Ecosystem

    script.
      var navMenu = document.getElementsByClassName('nav-menu')[0];
      var navToggleIcon = document.getElementsByClassName('nav-toggle-icon')[0];

      function toggleMobileMenu() {
        if (navMenu.className === 'nav-menu') {
          navMenu.className = 'nav-menu active';
          navToggleIcon.src = 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ionicons/4.5.6/collection/build/ionicons/svg/md-close.svg';
        } else {
          navMenu.className = 'nav-menu';
          navToggleIcon.src = 'https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ionicons/4.5.6/collection/build/ionicons/svg/md-menu.svg';
        }
      }
